title: 9 Chickweed Lane - 2000 through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"9 CHICKWEED LANE" Web Comic

"9 Chickweed Lane" (gocomics.com/9chickweedlane) by Brooke McEldowney follows the fortunes of the women of three generations of the Burber family -- Edna, Juliette, and Edda -- as they try to make their way in the world.  The strip premiered in 1993, and won Best Newspaper Comic at the 2006 National Cartoonists Society Awards.

This torrent includes "9 Chickweed Lane" comics from 2000 through the end of 2014 in a set of CBR files, one for each year.  (Earlier strips are unfortunately not available online.)  The torrent also includes a special "Hallmarks of Felinity" CBR, which collects all of the strip's HoF (and other specifically cat-centric) strips from 1999 through 2014 in a single volume.  

Most all of the strips through the end of 2013 were scanned by Starhome.  Later strips I downloaded myself.  The HoF volume I assembled myself, because I wanted all of the cat comics collected together.  (Those comics do, of course, also appear in the regular yearly CBRs.)
